AN UPDATE ON EXERCISM
\
Exercism itself has been going from strength to strength. Our wonderful team of maintainers continue to improve our content and exercises, and our mentors are always there to support you. In the next few days we will hit 3 million users (https://exercism.org/about/impact), which is a huge milestone.
\
I want to thank everyone who's been part of our journey so far. As the world of coding changes, we're here to try and help developers keep up to date with the skills they need, and enjoy all that programming has to offer!
